arch mailbox
event_close_plugin Python
event_close /onefang/python/PO/send.py
event_apply_plugin Python
event_apply /onefang/python/PO/receive.py
material 0
weight 0
no_pick 1
msg
Recieving Mail
-----------------------
Open the mailbox and get the scrolls,
read them by applying.

Sending Mail
-----------------------
Get a pen and be sure that you are
able to use the literacy skill. You can
get both, as well as mailscrolls at any 
post office, ask the clerk for help.
Mark a preadressed mailscroll,
and write on it with:
  mark mailscroll
  use_skill inscription <text>

You can write multiple lines, when done
drop the scoll in any mailbox and it
will be sent.
-----------------------
NOTE - Multiple lines doesn't
work yet.
endmsg
x 1
y 4
end
